Package psidev.psi.mi.jami.xml.model.extension.datasource

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PsiXmlSource<I extends Interaction>
    Interface for PSI-MI XML sources that can parse full PSI-MI XML files
    PsiXmlStreamSource<I extends Interaction>
    Interface for PSI-MI XML datasources that can stream PSI-MI XML files
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractPsiXmlBinarySource<T extends Interaction,B extends BinaryInteraction>
    Abstract class for Psi-XML 2.5 binary interaction data source which loads the full interaction dataset
    AbstractPsiXmlBinaryStream<T extends Interaction,B extends BinaryInteraction>
    Abstract class for binary interaction datasources
    AbstractPsiXmlSource<T extends Interaction>
    Abstract class for a PSI-XML 2.5 datasource that loads the full interaction dataset
    AbstractPsiXmlStream<T extends Interaction>
    Abstract class for psiXml data source
    DefaultPsiXmlSource
    Generic class for PSI-XML full datasource.
    DefaultPsiXmlStreamSource
    Generic class for PSI-XML streaming datasource.
    LightXmlBinarySource
    PSI-XML 2.5 data source that provides light binary interactions (no experimental details).
    LightXmlBinaryStreamSource
    Psi-XML 2.5 binary interaction datasource
    LightXmlSource
    PSI-XML 2.5 data source that provides light interactions (no experimental details).
    LightXmlStreamSource
    Datasource for PSI-xml 2.5 returning basic interactions
    XmlBinaryEvidenceSource
    PSI-XML 2.5 data source that provides binary interactions evidence (full experimental details).
    XmlBinaryEvidenceStreamSource
    PsiXml 2.5 datasource for binaryInteractionEvidence
    XmlBinarySource
    PSI-XML 2.5 data source that provides binary interactions (mixed of abstract interactions and interaction evidences).
    XmlBinaryStreamSource
    Psi-XML 2.5 mixed binary interaction datasource
    XmlComplexSource
    PSI-XML 2.5 data source that provides abstract interactions (ignore full experimental details).
    XmlComplexStreamSource
    Datasource for Psi-XML 2.5 abstract interactions
    XmlEvidenceSource
    PSI-XML 2.5 data source that provides interaction evidences (with full experimental details).
    XmlEvidenceStreamSource
    Datasource for Psi-xml 2.5 interaction evidence
    XmlModelledBinarySource
    PSI-XML 2.5 data source that provides modelled binary interactions (ignore experimental details).
    XmlModelledBinaryStreamSource
    Psi-xml 2.5 datasource for modelled binary interactions
    XmlModelledSource
    PSI-XML 2.5 data source that provides abstract interactions (ignore full experimental details).
    XmlModelledStreamSource
    Datasource for Psi-XML 2.5 abstract interactions
    XmlSource
    PSI-XML 2.5 data source that provides interactions (mix of abstract interactions and interaction evidences).
    XmlStreamSource
    Datasource for PSI-xml 2.5 returning mix of abstract interactions and interaction evidences
